{"tid":1509733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【亞馬遜森林大火】全球關注　李佳芯、黃翠如等多名TVB藝人發聲","createTime":"2019-08-27T02:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T17:38:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"df090c722cf878ea74188e20382ea63b90cf5d23","tid":1509733,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:47:19.000Z","msg":"有「地球之肺」之稱的亞馬遜森林是全球最大的熱帶雨林，在森林內生存了大概有300萬種植物和動物，以及100萬名原居民。亞馬遜森林大火發生至今已經約三個星期仍然未受控，巴西總統博爾索納羅亦已承諾派軍隊協助救火。而由於亞馬遜森林的生態對全球環境有莫大關連，所以今次大火亦引起國際性關注，多位國際名人亦先後發聲，包括荷里活影星里安納度狄卡比奧以及基斯坦奴朗拿度。<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然最近修例風波成為全港的焦點，但仍然有不少TVB藝人留意到大火的嚴重性</span>，紛紛在Instagram分享並表示關注，當中包括黃翠如、李佳芯、譚凱琪以及王浩信等。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/367796/%E4%BA%9E%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%9C%E6%A3%AE%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8-%E6%9D%8E%E4%BD%B3%E8%8A%AF-%E9%BB%83%E7%BF%A0%E5%A6%82%E7%AD%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8Dtvb%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2</code></pre>"},{"pid":"f251ce829b17ae2aee4504e00bb2b4600700851f","tid":1509733,"uid":39205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:47:30.000Z","msg":"呂麗乳搖呢？<br />\n<br />\n我成個腦都係個架撞緊埋黎嘅飛機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1509689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1509689</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"38017ac5bdd6b3de9c3ac2a5e32d2a0636a5b1e9","tid":1509733,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=4a8a33f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http